MUMBAI, INDIA - APRIL 30: Bollywood actor couple Aishwarya Rai Bachchan and husband Abhishek Bachchan at wedding reception of actor couple Bipasha Basu and Karan Singh on April 30, 2016 in Mumbai, India. Bipasha Basu got married to Karan Singh Grover on April 30 in a beautiful traditional Bengali wedding, attended by family and close friends. This is Bipasha’s first marriage, while Karan has been married twice before to Shraddha Nigam for 10 months and to Jennifer Winget for almost 2 years. (Photo by Pramod Thakur/Hindustan Times ) *** Please Use Credit from Credit Field ***
